Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:01.18,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Even the viewpoints of life and its meaningless proof
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:07.85,op trans,,0,0,0,,are nothing to you and cannot relieve your boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:13.07,op trans,,0,0,0,,The foolish people of that race, acting as leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:18.99,op trans,,0,0,0,,have written infantile theorems that stink of conceit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:25.08,op trans,,0,0,0,,Both our infinite love and dreams of that beyond the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:30.88,op trans,,0,0,0,,are granted freedoms of the imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:37.05,op trans,,0,0,0,,The finite cruelly allows time to flow on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.47,op trans,,0,0,0,,as I head towards my choice to renounce tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.01,op trans,,0,0,0,,Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:50.85,op trans,,0,0,0,,I mustn't pretend that I've made no promises
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.86,op trans,,0,0,0,,with my friends back in those brighter days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:02.78,op trans,,0,0,0,,So now I will deceive time itself with my remaining tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:09.08,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}as I am a solitary observer with no more doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:21.82,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}The tempting moment that connects our dream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:27.82,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}Permeates the blue skies after the violent storm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:33.96,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}Concealing itself within endless happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:40.24,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}The seed of grief cruelly tests us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:46.36,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}Actions and words of kindness that pass us by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:51.16,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}Shiver out of control in the dark of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:58.49,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}In the midst of a road filled with detours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:05.80,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}I realized what I must protect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:11.81,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}After passing through the suffering, our eyes call out to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:17.94,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}This is a bond founded by fate itself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:24.09,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}In a world full of things that are breaking apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:35.48,True End,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,200)}Our meeting is the only event that will last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now explain the parameters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of the final mission: Operation Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Modify the result without changing established history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The past consists of Makise Kurisu, lying in pool of blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and Okabe Rintarou seeing her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the past without changing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, pass me that screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling me "Dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, we only get one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough fuel for more than one trip to the past and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't be able to return to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never planned to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By changing the world line here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby changing the future, I won't need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:01:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail to change it, I'll have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably regret it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am the man who will destroy the ruling structure of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now commence Operation Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He made me laugh when he said, "The time is now,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and then had to run to the lab because he forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave the time machine there for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cyalume Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sticky red fluid in its core is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't know that was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to substitute it for Makise Kurisu's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On July 28th, if I see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,an unconscious Cristina lying in a pool of blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the past won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the idea behind Operation Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it makes sense, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem a little too easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Okarin made it sound like a greater force was at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma speaks even more dramatically
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when a plan is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see through his schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether to be impressed or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad scientist delusions again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that Kurisu person sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd get really excited and talk to Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mayushii wouldn't really understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you two fought all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but really, you were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu is a scientific genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She would never come to a lab like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she possesses the Reading Steiner too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But somewhere inside, she remembers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened in the other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone does, somewhere in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu did everything she could to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri... No, all of us can be here now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because of Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin? Do you like Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cristina is my assistant, my dear friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and very special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's in love with me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Okarin gets a real girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, um... Miss Amane...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who was my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've managed to arrive at exactly the same time as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the Cyalume Saber where I asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Modify the result without changing the established past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For that to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this is where I begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know the overall effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but if I get the metal Upa here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it diminishes the odds of any metal ending up in that folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many left of this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mayushii's out of 100-yen coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so spoiled, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I've known you since we were kids, I'm not lending you any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how harsh life can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Upa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not rare, but isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nakabachi's press conference
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will now begin in the eighth floor hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never imagined I'd have to pretend to be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kurisu picked up the Upa that Mayuri dropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But since it isn't metal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that paper will burn in the plane accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that's left is dealing with Nakabachi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and finding a chance to knock out Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The liquid dried up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't used it for such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that air got inside and dried out the liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Daddy, I wanted you to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There has to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting rid of Nakabachi won't be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the blood will be problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there was just something I could substitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call it stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who yearns for chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One who will destroy the ruling structure of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the man who will send your ambitions to oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You worked together to sabotage my press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring that knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do my godlike powers strike fear in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. You're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on insulting me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're just a small, pathetic man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A man too petty to appreciate his own daughter's talent can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's what you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie down. I'll call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this emergency services?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I need someone here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is, without a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Kurisu I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you wait just a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll bleed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're about to begin the longest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}most important three weeks of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It all went just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get back, you'll need to go to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be hard, but try to hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Steins Gate world line is completely unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if your theory is correct, the paper will burn, so the time machine arms race won't come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither will World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll say thank you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,850)}I'll see you in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That paper would've completely changed mankind's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a paper for the creation of a time machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's gone... Burnt up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His words were unclear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Russian government has denied everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Okarin here, Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When he came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This badge identifies you as Lab Member 006.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I become a lab member?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those memories may rest in your other life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get something, Faris?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This badge is for Lab Member 007.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you desire my aid, hold the badge and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"La Yohda Stasella." Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be working here as a part-timer, from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiryuu Moeka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She helped Nae after she fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't have a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so she'll be working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiina Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe started hitting on her the minute he saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Visit the lab whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Welcome back-arin!}Oh, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do "oh, come in" and "Okarin" sound that similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,These?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they're lab member badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lab Member 002 and 003!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we get so many lab members?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they go up to 008.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin's "O."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina, Hashida, Urushibara, Faris...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are "M," "K," and "A"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He had another one that he put in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lab Member 008 will arrive in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More delusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an inevitable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your inevitable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years? I can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think the lab will change,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many years go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you writing a paper for an American research lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you working all night on some experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may still be thinking of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't remember the three weeks we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, you're breathing, speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thinking your hardest about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're observing the same world I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this world with an unknown future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I protected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's its choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,El Psy Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,El Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet again, Cristina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm not Cristina, and I'm {\i1}not{\i0} your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome my assistant, Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Cristina.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one knows what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has infinite potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}proven by this encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,622)}This is surely the choice of Steins Gate.
